gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 123, Raptors 89
gameRecap.excerpt: Sacramento defeated Toronto, 123-89, as they improved to 40-28 on the year. De'Aaron Fox led the Kings with a game-high 20 points, along with four rebounds, and five assists as Domantas Sabonis added 13 points, 17 rebounds, and 10 assists. Gary Trent Jr. led the Raptors with 18 points and six rebounds. Toronto moves to 23-46 on the year.
